name: The Internationals
overview: In 2001, a gang of Colombian thieves travel to Argentina to carry out robberies while the country is preoccupied with a political and economic crisis.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Fausto, a Colombian thief, recruits a few 'colleagues' for his gang of international thieves and heads to Argentina, aiming to take advantage of the ongoing social crisis. However, he is hiding the real reason for his trip...

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Right after their arrival at Buenos Aires, Jennifer is arrested. Meanwhile, Fausto robs a hotel while the rest of the gang watch and learn. Things take a turn for the worse, when Tino and Mario decide to steal a motorcycle.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Tino has a bullet lodged in his shoulder, and Susy desperately searches for someone to help him. Fausto finally reunites with Mafe, but things don't go as he would have liked. Later on, the gang carries out a successful robbery.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Fausto manages to escape from Castillo, while Walter discovers that Marta Costas needs Romero's influence. Later on, Fausto confesses the real reason behind his arrival in Argentina, but he keeps his bond with Mafe a secret.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Castillo kills Mayer, while Fausto offers to steal from Romero everything Marta needs in exchange for his freedom. Later on, Fausto makes a shocking discovery about Romero's endeavors, while looking through his computer.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: The gang goes to a real estate agency for a robbery, but things get complicated when Tino appears carrying a gun. Fausto defuses the situation and the robbery is completed with success... until the moment Castillo arrives.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: The pension where the gang is hiding is raided, at the same moment that Walter realizes that Fausto has betrayed his father. And as a number of shocking discoveries starts breaking the gang apart, Fausto decides to visit his son.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Fausto escapes and manages to steal invaluable diamonds from Castillo. Meanwhile, as the gang prepares to leave the country, an unexpected turn of events changes the course of their plan.
